{"type": "article", "id": 25437, "title": "可调整高度的椅子", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-14T06:59:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160608130747Dwgl9YH0b56BjAaN.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">在小空间里设计家具已成为目前的热点，荷兰设计师 Sander Lorier 还推出了这张可调节高度的椅子。它由一个带羊毛垫的座位和三角腿的支架结构组成，通过绿色的带子来升降。设计师想要让它适合餐厅、书房等不同空间，借此给居住在小空间的人更多的适用性。售价 1299 欧元，<a href=\"http://studiolorier.com/product/hybrid-chair/\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130744URmLchCdk5DH3nxW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130744F5DNUJeh1dtXLOPr.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130745EoztK7paWbZNAVnu.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7475\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608130746DA40ICt3NvWqFYQU.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7475\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}